---
title: Easy Lamb Pasanda Style Curry with Buttery Bulgur, Peas, Yoghurt and Mango Chutney
description: Pasanda curries are fragrant and gently spiced Indian dishes that are usually rich and creamy. Here, we've got lamb and peas, perfect for soaking up the delicious flavour of the pasanda curry sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R15_W37_UK_QR25534-4_Main_low_2-29432297.jpg
